public interface Coverage
extends Clause, Clause
    Coverage A coverage is specific cause of loss or insurable object within a single PolicyLine. This table contains coverage (boolean) and coverage attribute information spanning policyline. Policyline is differentiated by approximately 5 dozen sub-type entities.
